properties.name: ReplaceCurtainWalls
properties.description: Set to true if you want to replace curtain walls to have openings the same size as the wall. This is useful for IES exports. Default false  This is a Boolean  ReplaceCurtainWalls is a Property of BH.oM.XML.Settings.XMLSettings

properties.name: ReplaceSolidOpeningsIntoDoors
properties.description: Set to true if you want to replace an opening which is marked as solid into a door. Useful for IES exports. Default false  This is a Boolean  ReplaceSolidOpeningsIntoDoors is a Property of BH.oM.XML.Settings.XMLSettings

properties.name: IncludeConstructions
properties.description: Set to true if you want to include construction and material data in the export. Default false  This is a Boolean  IncludeConstructions is a Property of BH.oM.XML.Settings.XMLSettings

properties.name: FixIncorrectAirTypes
properties.description: Set to true if you want air types with one adjacent space (i.e. external air walls) to have their type fixed based on their tilt. Default false  This is a Boolean  FixIncorrectAirTypes is a Property of BH.oM.XML.Settings.XMLSettings

properties.name: NewFile
properties.description: Set to false if you want to append to a file when pushing XML. If set to true then a file will be created. If a file exists, it will be overwritten. Default true  This is a Boolean  NewFile is a Property of BH.oM.XML.Settings.XMLSettings

properties.name: UnitType
properties.description: Set the unit type for the export to be either SI or Imperial. Default SI  This is a BH.oM.XML.Enums.UnitType  UnitType is a Property of BH.oM.XML.Settings.XMLSettings

properties.name: ExportDetail
properties.description: Set the detail of your export to be either full (whole building), shell (exterior walls only), or spaces (each individual space as its own XML file). Default full  This is a BH.oM.XML.Enums.ExportDetail  ExportDetail is a Property of BH.oM.XML.Settings.XMLSettings

properties.name: DistanceTolerance

properties.name: PlanarTolerance

properties.name: OffsetDistance
properties.description: Set a distance to offset openings that have a area >= the area of the host panel. Value should be negative. Defaults to -0.001  This is a Double  OffsetDistance is a Property of BH.oM.XML.Settings.XMLSettings
